HEADWORD: Subdued
<hw>Sub*dued"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Conquered; overpowered; crushed; submissive; mild.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not glaring in color; soft in tone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

